# Docs Standards

## Allowed Scope
- `docs/**/*.md`
- `.cursor/**/*.md`

## Forbidden Scope
- Runtime implementation in `src/**` or `functions/**`

## Priorities
- Keep text concise, explicit, and testable.
- Align terminology across requirements and specs.
- Keep acceptance criteria concrete and verifiable.
- Limit edits to the requested documentation scope.

## Boundary Enforcement
- Do not implement runtime behavior in docs tasks.
- If runtime work is needed, hand off to `frontend-gemschi` or `backend-gemschi`.
